        <mxCell id="p3" value="Mar/25&#xa;R$500&#xa;PAGO" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=9;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="160" y="170" width="60" height="45" as="geometry"/>
